Package org.jsapar.text

Text formatting and parsing.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanFormat
    Format class that can be used to parse or format boolean values based on a true and a false value.
    RegExpFormat
    A formatter that while both parsing and formatting, checks that the value matches supplied regex pattern.
